CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A9 reads: "With Iota Speaker - Glamorous television personality, Eleanor Schano, right, was guest speaker at the annual Business Week luncheon of Pi Chapter, Iota Phi Lambda Sorority, last Saturday afternoon. She is seen here with Sorors Carrie Ann Dix, chairman; Jean Farrish and Marilyn Baldwin, co-chairman. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Iota Phi Lambda sorority members, including Eleanor Schano, right, posed with Carrie Ann Dix, Jean Farrish, and Marilyn Baldwin in front of staircase in Eastern Star home, Brushton Avenue
